<div class="title">Meeting my Light</div>
<div class="substance">5-MeO-DMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Fallenangel&Exact=1">Fallenangel</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Fallenangel. "Meeting my Light: An Experience with 5-MeO-DMT (exp26349)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 10, 2008. erowid.org/exp/26349</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

